law.history: Repealed 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 201, sec. 23. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 112, secs. 1 and 2. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 762b-6.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Division to enforce fire prevention laws of state and political subdivisions.
